# {{ project_name }}

{{ description }}

A Forge **substrate star** — a thin per-substrate repo whose runtime is declared
as `kreuzwerker/docker` resources and deployed through **Nereus** (OpenTofu),
never hand-composed. Health is judged by **Nyx**, so this layer stays dumb.

## Layout

| File | Role |
| :-- | :-- |
| `star.toml` | the star manifest (identity, tier, seams) |
| `versions.tf` | Tofu + provider pins (`kreuzwerker/docker`) |
| `providers.tf` | docker daemon connection (`var.docker_host`) |
| `variables.tf` | inputs (the nas01 daemon endpoint) |
| `main.tf` | the runtime resources (authored per feature) |

## Deploy

```bash
tofu init
tofu plan      # show drift
tofu apply     # place containers on nas01
```

State lives in the shared Nereus PG backend, not here.
